    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Bernát Sárkány, Gábor Rajki, Antal Sárkány, István
                    Gosztonyi, Péter Ivánczy, Farkas Ivánczy, Lénárd Gosztonyi, and other friends
                    (Prague, 27 July 1549)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">He has intervened with the King in their interest and
                            arranged for the ispáns to be sent there by Saint Michael’s day. He is
                            surprised that the investigation has been dragged out this long because
                            the King sent the commissioners there a long time ago, and they should
                            have finished already. </p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Egregii Domini,<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1">Bernát Sárkány,
                        Gábor Rajki, Antal Sárkány, István Gosztonyi, Péter Ivánczy, Farkas Ivánczy,
                        Lénárd Gosztonyi and other friends.</note> Amici nobis Honorandi, salutem! </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Ea, quae Dominationes Vestrae nobis scribunt, intelleximus. Nos pro
                    negotio earundem apud <persName>regiam maiestatem</persName> satis superque
                    laboravimus et perficiemus, ut ad festum sancti Michaelis archangeli<note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.2">29 September.</note> proxime venturum
                    commissarii illuc mittantur ad determinandum Dominationum Vestrarum omne
                    negotium. Quod autem revisio illius hactenus dilata sit, miramur, nam
                    commissarii <persName>maiestatis regiae</persName>, domini nostri clementissimi
                    quia antea istuc iussi erant, potuissent Dominationum Vestrarum negotia finire.
                    Dominationes Vestras feliciter valere optamus.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Praga</placeName> 27. Iulii anno Domini 1549.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">
                    <seg type="signature">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Agriensis cancellarius regiae
                        maiestatis manu propria</seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.5">Egregiis dominis Bernardo Sarkan, Gabrieli Rayky, Anthonio Sarkan,
                    Stephano Gostony, Petro Iwanchy, Wolffgango Iwanchy et Leonardo Gostony et
                    amicis nobis honorandis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
